WEBVTT

01:14.060 --> 01:16.130
WOMAN:
There is darkness...

01:21.100 --> 01:23.091
.. and there is light.

01:39.540 --> 01:41.815
There are men and women.

01:45.700 --> 01:48.658
There 's food.

01:53.900 --> 01:56.130
There are restaurants.

02:01.180 --> 02:02.977
Disease.

02:12.380 --> 02:14.371
There 's work.

02:19.660 --> 02:22.128
Traffic.

02:25.500 --> 02:28.014
The days as we know them.

02:31.740 --> 02:34.015
