I have a tough time sleeping
with someone else in the bed.

03:25.820 --> 03:27.572
Are you kicking me out?

03:27.620 --> 03:29.770
I have to go to work soon anyway.

03:31.740 --> 03:34.652
We dance and drink all night,
we go back to your place, you fuck me

03:34.740 --> 03:36.935
and now you wake me up
and kick me out?

03:36.980 --> 03:39.448
I can't sleep
with another person in the bed.

03:41.180 --> 03:44.217
- That's funny.
- That's just the way it is.

03:48.540 --> 03:50.531
[cry of seagulls]

03:52.460 --> 03:55.020
I didn't know
you'd started smoking again.

04:06.980 --> 04:09.016
What do you feel like doing?

04:10.180 --> 04:12.171
Throwing stones.

04:14.820 --> 04:16.094
At what?

04:18.860 --> 04:20.976
Seagulls.

04:28.620 --> 04:30.611
Sweetheart.

04:33.100 --> 04:35.660
- You'll find someone.
- Shut up and throw.

