04:58.460 --> 05:00.178
Come on.

05:00.300 --> 05:02.450
Poor baby.

05:54.180 --> 05:56.171
Lebanon?

05:57.580 --> 05:59.571
Morocco.

06:01.540 --> 06:03.610
Morocco.

06:08.940 --> 06:10.771
Now that's funny.

06:11.580 --> 06:15.255
- What's funny?
- Seeing you today.

06:15.340 --> 06:16.693
Hilarious.

06:16.740 --> 06:20.415
Come with me for a minute, will you?
They want us at the hospital.

06:21.940 --> 06:24.454
Aren't you going to ask
why I haven't been to work?

06:24.500 --> 06:28.334
- Well, you've been sick.
- Not sick, just unhappy.

06:29.940 --> 06:31.976
Well, it's the same thing.

06:32.060 --> 06:34.096
Unhappy on account of a man.

06:34.740 --> 06:36.731
No kidding?

06:37.460 --> 06:39.735
So what are we wanted for?

06:39.780 --> 06:42.135
Er, to see a patient.

06:42.180 --> 06:44.250
- Why?
- What's going on?

06:44.300 --> 06:45.892
Well, we're just going to find out.

06:45.980 --> 06:49.131
- You know he's really pissed off in there.
- Excuse me.

06:49.180 --> 06:50.659
When can I take him back home?

06:51.860 --> 06:54.852
Oh, well, we just need
to talk to him, so...

06:54.900 --> 06:57.289
- He needs to explain it all again?
- Well...

06:57.340 --> 06:58.853
Look. Look, listen.

06:58.900 --> 07:01.972
He called me up, right,
and he told me he was coming home...

07:02.020 --> 07:06.457
and then all of a sudden his voice breaks
and he bursts into tears.

07:06.500 --> 07:07.774
Mm-hm.

07:07.820 --> 07:11.779
And then he starts telling me
that he doesn't see any meaning to life.

07:11.820 --> 07:15.096
I mean, he's not usually like that.
He's a truck driver.

07:15.140 --> 07:16.175
OK.

07:16.220 --> 07:19.690
And then he pulls over at the side
and says he's fine again.

07:19.740 --> 07:23.938
- Except, he cannae smell any more.
- He can't smell any more?

07:24.020 --> 07:26.215
Well, I told him to find a hospital

07:26.260 --> 07:28.854
because, you know,
that isn't normal, is it?

07:39.020 --> 07:41.898
Hello, er... Donald.

07:42.660 --> 07:44.776
Stephen Montgomery here again.

07:49.620 --> 07:52.657
- Hi, I'm Susan.
- Hello, Stephen. Hello, Susan.

07:53.820 --> 07:56.573
- You can't smell any more?
- That's right, Susan.

07:56.620 --> 07:58.497
I can 't smell any more.

07:58.540 --> 08:00.974
But is your mood back to normal?

08:01.060 --> 08:04.052
I've been sitting here for nearly
11 hours. My mood is not great.

08:06.420 --> 08:09.332
But you don 't feel any discomfort
other than a lack of smell?

08:09.380 --> 08:10.859
No, Susan.

08:10.900 --> 08:14.939
And has anybody else in your family
or at work had similar experiences?

08:14.980 --> 08:17.972
I haven't got a clue
cos I'm sitting here, aren't l?

08:22.620 --> 08:26.249
- What do you want from me?
- I just want your opinion.

08:26.340 --> 08:30.299
I'm an epidemiologist, Stephen.
So why am I talking to this guy?

08:30.340 --> 08:33.251
Cos we've got seven more
just like him in Aberdeen.

08:33.299 --> 08:34.938
Five in Dundee.

08:34.980 --> 08:38.450
11 right here in Glasgow.
18 in Edinburgh.

08:38.500 --> 08:41.094
There's over 100 reported cases
in England.

08:41.140 --> 08:45.019
They've got them in France,
Belgium, ltaly, Spain.

08:46.540 --> 08:49.213
They've all appeared
in the last 24 hours.

08:52.900 --> 08:54.891
How were they infected?

08:55.820 --> 08:57.856
I'm not sure they are.

08:57.900 --> 08:59.652
Meaning?

09:00.500 --> 09:05.972
Well, all the early indications suggest
no connection between them at all.

09:06.020 --> 09:08.215
No contact. No pattern. Nothing.

09:09.460 --> 09:11.496
[glass mutes voice]

09:14.100 --> 09:17.251
Is my wife still out there?
Let me speak to my wife.

09:17.300 --> 09:19.575
Please, let me speak to my wife.

09:22.380 --> 09:24.371
[glass mutes voice]

09:27.580 --> 09:29.730
STEPH EN :
Maybe it'll just go away.

09:34.940 --> 09:37.534
- So we won't panic.
- Hm.

09:40.180 --> 09:42.171
[chatter and laughter]

09:46.660 --> 09:49.254
Michael, that's a table of 12
just sat down.

09:49.380 --> 09:51.132
- Where are they, at the bar?
- Yeah.

09:51.140 --> 09:54.416
