Nothing that matches anything we know.

13:13.060 --> 13:16.177
But it's fair to say
it isn't obviously contagious.

13:16.220 --> 13:17.972
It's fair to say it's spreading.

13:18.700 --> 13:20.019
OK.

13:20.060 --> 13:23.655
