17:30.460 --> 17:32.451
- Good night.
- See you later.

17:32.500 --> 17:34.377
- See you later, boss.
- Cheers, boys.

17:34.420 --> 17:36.012
Good night.

17:38.020 --> 17:40.215
- Keep smiling.
- Good night, James.

17:56.420 --> 18:00.174
- Got your own smokes tonight, sailor?
- I'm still a chef.

18:03.940 --> 18:06.170
My dad called everybody sailor.

18:06.220 --> 18:08.495
He worked in the docks all his life.

18:08.540 --> 18:11.691
He never went sailing anywhere
but he called everybody sailor.

18:11.740 --> 18:13.219
All right.

18:13.260 --> 18:16.889
Even people he didn't know.
"Hello, sailor." "Goodbye, sailor."

18:16.940 --> 18:21.411
