21:13.620 --> 21:17.249
Look... Would you... Would you like me
to take you back to your home?

21:17.340 --> 21:18.932
Yeah? Come on.

21:18.940 --> 21:21.329
You take the cloth. I'll get the...

21:21.380 --> 21:23.177
