26:13.100 --> 26:14.328
Oregano.

26:17.700 --> 26:20.055
Richard, can you get me a clean apple?

26:23.060 --> 26:25.130
Life goes on.

26:26.460 --> 26:28.735
The food becomes spicier...

26:29.540 --> 26:31.371
