that are no longer triggered.

26:46.140 --> 26:47.129
Ooh-hoo!

26:47.180 --> 26:49.933
Smell and memory
were connected in the brain.

26:51.420 --> 26:55.015
Cinnamon might have reminded you
of your grandmother's apron.

26:55.060 --> 26:58.939
The scent of cut hay
could evoke a childhood fear of cows.

27:00.420 --> 27:04.254
