and life goes on.

49:58.260 --> 50:00.979
People do what they did before
as best they can.

50:12.100 --> 50:13.852
[crunches]

50:18.780 --> 50:20.771
[crunches]

50:22.140 --> 50:25.894
Within a few weeks,
taste becomes a distant memory.

50:26.260 --> 50:28.979
